import React from "react";
import { Redirect } from "react-router-dom";
import Dashboard from '../pages/Writer/WriterDashboard/index'
import Exam from '../pages/Writer/Exam/index'
import Questions from '../pages/Writer/Exam/Questions'
import Library from '../pages/Writer/Library/Index'
import Profile from '../pages/Writer/Profile/index'
import Projects from '../pages/Writer/Projects/index'
import SubmitProject from '../pages/Writer/Projects/SubmitProject'
import ProjectPage from '../pages/Writer/Projects/Projectpage'
import Wallet from '../pages/Writer/Wallet/index'

const writerRoutes = [
    // writers Dashboard
    { path: "/wdashboard", component: Dashboard },
    { path: "/wexam", component: Exam },
    { path: "/wquestion/:id?", component: Questions },
    { path: "/wlibrary", component: Library },
    { path: "/writerprofile", component: Profile },
    { path: "/wallet", component: Wallet },
    { path: "/wprojects", component: Projects },
    
    { path: "/wprojectspage/:id?", component: ProjectPage },

    { path: "/", exact: true, component: () => <Redirect to="/wdashboard" /> }
  ];

export { writerRoutes };
